.description
Revenge of the Blob, an animated interpretation using Bill Watterson's
original cartoon strip character "Calvin".  Tells the story of Calvin's
encounter with his mother's food, and how the dreaded tapioca monster gets
back at Calvin for turning his nose up at it.  
